lowers to brew potions and tame spirits. Cultivate ingredients to cook your fave dishes for fun and stat bonuses! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Customize and decorate your home to make it uniquely yours with over 300 decorations </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/explorev4.gif?t=1734539285\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Travel by balloon, broom, and glider through unique biomes to reach the outer edges of the world to uncover the secrets of your floating home in the sky</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Tame and befriend wild spirits to fight alongside you - Over 70 Spirits to tame!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Discover and explore dungeons to earn upgrades, collect loot and uncover secrets - Or take on the INFINIDUNGEON for neverending battles and rewards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Optimize your character with unique skills and upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Craft dozens of items and vehicles to prepare for the treacherous wilderness</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/updatesSinceLaunch.gif?t=1734539285\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Since we launched on September 20, 2023 we\u2019ve been working hard to add more functionality and fun to the game, including:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cooking!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">41 new cards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 50 new and free decorative items!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marriage!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Infinidungeon!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More QoL improvements than we can count!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">+ More updates coming over 2024 and 